    "en": {
      "title": "Important meeting suddenly cancelled",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Indian High Commissioner Gopal Bagle had decided to pay a visit to Kandy yesterday (27), but suddenly this visit has been cancelled.",
        "While the Chinese Ambassador visited the Malwattu-Askiriya Mahanayake Theras yesterday at 4.30 pm, the Indian High Commissioner to Sri Lanka Gopal Bagley had also decided to meet the Malwattu-Askiriya Mahanayake Theras at 3.30 pm yesterday.",
        "In this regard, when asked the Indian Assistant High Commissioner in Kandy, he said that the meeting was canceled due to the sudden illness of Indian High Commissioner Gopal Bagle."
      ],
